------------------------------
          Quark
------------------------------

Quark is a lightweight GPU rendered text editor.
*This is an early-stage project*

* Supports Linux only for now *

------------------------------
Build Instructions
------------------------------


Linux:
  Prerequisites:
  -> clang
	-> cmake ( for glfw3 )
  
  1. run ./scripts/build_static_library.sh
     to compile glfw3
  2. Build:
         ./build_linux.sh
